== SOURCE

https://towardsdatascience.com/machine-learning-in-the-world-of-blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-68651ebaecd7

== AGENT

Thomas E. Koker and Dimitrios Koutmos; Taotao Wang, Soung Chang Liew, and Shengli Zhang

== GOAL

To create profitable crypto trading bots and Optimising blockchain mining strategy

== DATA

Common blockchain mining strategies

== METHODS

Direct reinforcement learning and multi-dimensional reinforcement learning

== RESULTS

Profitable trading bots and optimisation of crytocurrency mining strategies.

== ISSUES

Had trouble optimising mining strategies for mining reward when blockchain mining rewards
can vary due to many different uncontrollable factors.

== SCORE

6

== COMMENTS

Was interesting to see machine learning isn't just used for crypto price predictions and trading bots but
for mining strategies too. 
